column2: SELECT    ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY g) #, p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z,    ((p.g + #*(p.g - p.r) + #)) as B,    p.fracDev_g, p.petroRad_g as PRadius, p.petroR9#_g as PRadius9#, p.expAB_g as ratioba, p.expRad_g as efscale,    p.deVRad_g as vfscale,    s.z as redshift,    ((p.g + #*(p.g - p.r) + #) + (#*LOG1#(#*PI()*(p.petroR9#_r)*(p.petroR9#_r))) + (#*LOG1#(p.expAB_r)) -(#*LOG1#(#+s.z))) as moB,    (s.z*(#/#)) as Distancepc,     ((p.g + #*(p.g - p.r) + #) - #*(LOG1#((s.z*(#/#))))) as MB,   dbo.fGetUrlNavId(objid) as link into mydb.LSBG from photoObj p   JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID   JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust st ON st.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE     p.type = #    AND p.r <= #    AND p.expAB_g > #    AND s.z BETWEEN # AND #    AND ((p.g + #*(p.g - p.r) + #) + (#*LOG1#(#*#*(p.petroR9#_r)*(p.petroR9#_r))) + (#*LOG1#(p.expAB_r)) -(#*LOG1#(#+s.z))) BETWEEN # AND # ORDER BY    p.r, #
